1)Prerequisuites is Crosscompile the Xbee ansic library for BBB using the doc crosscompilation_BBB
2)copy the Transparent client to the BBB using SCP or direct copy
3)Execute it by ./Transparent client /dev/ttyS1
4)Before Step 3 we ahve to ensure the Baud rate fixed is stty -F /dev/ttyS1 115200 raw -echo
5)If everything is ok, the Pan id and version is displayed else cross cheeck the connections and POwercycle the device
6)ttyS1 is pins24 and pins26
7)ttyS2 is pins 22 and pins21
8) To ensure succesfull UART bring up check with dmesg | grep tty and also follow the Doc XBEE_UART_Steps
